Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:04.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Day and night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:07.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}We searched along the rails
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:10.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Hoping to find another trail
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:12.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Leading to heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:15.03,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}The heavens are waiting for motion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:17.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Fired up for action
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:18.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}There's no gain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:19.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:20.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:21.16,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:21.91,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:22.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}All this pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:24.91,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}My pains don't exist to entertain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:27.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Count with me, one two three
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:30.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many liters can you bleed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:34.55,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many turns you plan to last?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:37.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many lives you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:39.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I saw a star
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:42.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Brightening up the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:51.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}So don't you stop my fires from burning our everything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:56.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}You and me are nothing but temporary
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:03:01.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Don't you start begging for mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:03.12,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}For when I win
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:04.87,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I won't forgive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:06.41,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}And I shall win
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:07.95,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}And I shall win
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:14.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Yes, I shall win your one-sided game
